<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عُثْمَانُ بْنُ الْوَلِيدِ الْقُرَشِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(البسيط)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - وَكُلُّ ذِي جِدَّة لا بُدَّ مُدْرِكُهُ ... رَيْبُ الزَّمَانِ الَّذِي فِي صَرْفِهِ غِيَرُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٩٦)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقالَ عَمْرُو بْنُ دَارَةَ:</span> <span class="c2">(السريع)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - كُلُّ بَنِي أُمٍّ وإِنْ أَكْثَرَتْ ... يَوْماً يَصِيروُنَ إِلَى وَاحِدِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٩٧)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ عَبْدِ الأَعْلَى الشَّيْبَانِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(مجزوء الرمل)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١ - كُلُّ حَيٍّ ذِي اجْتِمَاعٍ ... رَهْنُ بَيْن وَشَتَاتِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٩٨)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ صَالِحُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْقُدُّوس:</span> <span class="c2">(الوافر)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١ - كُلُّ أَخِي ثَراءٍ سَوفَ يُمْسِي ... فَقِيرًا وَالجَمِيعُ إِلَى شَتَاتِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٩٩)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وَقالَ أَيْضاً:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١ - وَكُلُّ جَميعٍ في نَعِيمٍ وَغِبْطَةٍ ... رَهِينَةُ بَيْنٍ عَاجلٍ وَشَتَاتِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١١٠٠)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ الْقُطَامِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(البسيط)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>